title: Rugger blacklist bot integration
body: Once Rugpuller database integration is done, should the "Is it SAFU?" bot (Honeypot tester) be freely accessible to the public, so that the whole Polygon community benefits from the rugpuller database, or should it remain a Tier 2 Premium tool for SAFU holders?
choices: No, keep it as a premium tool
author: 0xf7e3dE13d5dfD9165594cE87e520fC922125afbb
